HOTEL_PLAZA
Congrats! You reach your way in the Final Revelation Plaza, a serene garden bathed in an ethereal glow. Ancient statues line the periphery, each holding a cryptic symbol. The air is charged with a mix of anticipation and tranquility. At the center stands an ancient, overgrown tree with shimmering leaves. Each leaf holds a fragment of the hotel's secrets. As you approach, the leaves begin to unfurl, revealing the interconnected tales of guests, staff, and the hotel's mysterious past. The fountain in the heart of the plaza springs to life, its water reflecting the journey you've undertaken. ROLL THE CREDITS!
#
HOTEL_SECRET_CHAMBER
You stumble upon a clandestine room hidden on the second floor, the Secret Escape Chamber. Dimly lit, the air in this chamber is tinged with secrecy. In one corner, a sturdy ladder reaches upward, disappearing into darkness. The sound of distant footsteps echoes through the stone walls, emphasizing the covert nature of this discovery.
